EV isolated method: To isolate exosomes, all samples were filtered through 0.22 µM filters. Exosomes were isolated from the serum sample using ExoQuick Exosome Precipitation Solution (System Biosciences, CA, USA).
Project_Description: In our study, the exosomal microRNA expression profiles between PCOS patients and non PCOS individuals were comparatively and comprehensively analyzed.
